                                    <div class="news-tab-anchor">
                                        <a href="https://www.microchip.com/en-us/about/news-releases/products/new-bzpack-msic-power-modules-designed-for-demanding-applications" target="_blank" aria-label="Learn more about New BZPACK mSiC® Power Modules Are Designed for Demanding Applications in Harsh Environments"> <i class="fas fa-long-arrow-right"></i> Learn more"</a>
