                            </div>
                            <div class="homepage-card-content">
                                <div class="newstab-card-content">
                                    <div class="newstab-card-title" data-tooltip="Product Roundup: March 2026" data-tooltip-position="top-center">
                                        Product Roundup: March 2026
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="newstab-card-desc">Microchip's Product Roundup features a selection of our latest products, reference designs and software solutions. Explore how these innovative technologies can elevate your next design project.</div>
                                    <div class="news-tab-anchor">
                                        <a href="https://www.microchip.com/en-us/about/media-center/blog/2026/product-roundup-march-2026" target="_blank" aria-label="Learn more about Product Roundup: March 2026"> <i class="fas fa-long-arrow-right"></i> Learn more"</a>
