                                    </div>
                                    <div class="newstab-card-desc">Join us at the IEEE MTT-S International Microwave Symposium (IMS) 2025 in Boston, MA, June 9–11, where innovation meets RF and microwave excellence.</div>
                                    <div class="news-tab-anchor">
                                        <a href="https://www.microchip.com/en-us/about/events-info/ims" target="_blank" aria-label="Learn more about International Microwave Symposium (IMS) 2026"> <i class="fas fa-long-arrow-right"></i> Learn More"</a>
